OL,3,CPontins owner denies corporate
OL,4,Cmanslaughter after roof collapse at
OL,5,Choliday park
OL,7,FThe owner of Pontins holiday parks has
OL,8,Fpleaded not guilty to corporate
OL,9,Fmanslaughter after an air conditioning
OL,10,Fduct fell on guests at a resort in
OL,11,FSomerset.
OL,13,FWendy Jones, 68, died in August 2019
OL,14,Fafter spending six months in hospital
OL,15,Ffollowing the incident at the Brean
OL,16,FSands resort.
