OL,3,CPontins owner denies corporate
OL,4,Cmanslaughter after roof collapse at
OL,5,Choliday park
OL,7,FShe was among 18 people injured when
OL,8,Fapproximately 40 metres of structural
OL,9,Fducting and ceiling collapsed into the
OL,10,Fbar area inside the entertainment
OL,11,Fcentre, called The Fun Factory, in
OL,12,FFebruary 2019.
OL,14,FBritannia Jinky Jersey Ltd, the parent
OL,15,Fcompany of Pontins, appeared before
OL,16,FBristol Crown Court on Wednesday for a
OL,17,Fplea and trial preparation hearing.
