OL,3,CPontins owner denies corporate
OL,4,Cmanslaughter after roof collapse at
OL,5,Choliday park
OL,7,FJudge Julian Lambert confirmed that
OL,8,Fthe company had pleaded not guilty to
OL,9,Fthe two charges it faces, corporate
OL,10,Fmanslaughter and failing to discharge
OL,11,Fa duty under the Health and Safety at
OL,12,FWork etc Act.
OL,14,FIt is alleged that, between 1 January
OL,15,F2015 and 5 August 2019, Britannia
OL,16,FJinky Jersey Ltd "managed and
OL,17,Forganised its activities in such a way
OL,18,Fas to cause the death of Wendy Jones".
