OL,3,CPontins owner denies corporate
OL,4,Cmanslaughter after roof collapse at
OL,5,Choliday park
OL,7,FThe company is said to have "exposed
OL,8,FWendy Jones to the risk of death from
OL,9,Fthe collapse of ventilation ducting,
OL,10,Fwhich was positioned at height in the
OL,11,FFun Factory at Pontins Brean Sands, in
OL,12,Fgross breach of its duty to take
OL,13,Freasonable care for the safety of
OL,14,FWendy Jones".
OL,16,FThe second charge alleges that,
OL,17,Fbetween 1 January 2015 and 21 February
OL,18,F2019, it failed to ensure that members
OL,19,Fof the public were not exposed to
OL,20,Frisks to their health and safety.
