OL,7,FIt names the risk posed as "the
OL,8,Finstallation of soundproofing
OL,9,Fmaterials in the Fun Factory at
OL,10,FPontins Brean Sands".
OL,12,FJudge Lambert said a trial, expected
OL,13,Fto last up to six weeks, would take
OL,14,Fplace at Bristol Crown Court on 12
OL,15,FOctober next year. He added that a pre-
OL,16,Ftrial hearing would take place on a
OL,17,Fdate to be fixed.
